---json
{
  "layout": "layouts/t-mofu.njk",
  "permalink": "/reviews/",
  "slug": "reviews",
  "tierClass": "section--tier-hub",
  "callBar": false,
  "bodyClass": "page--trust",
  "title": "Client Reviews · Verified on Clutch · TechBrot",
  "description": "Verified TechBrot client reviews on Clutch. Two real, documented engagements — no fabricated testimonials, no inflated star counts, no AggregateRating until we have five or more verified reviews.",
  "breadcrumb": [
    { "name": "Home", "href": "/" },
    { "name": "Reviews" }
  ],
  "hero": {
    "eyebrow": "Client reviews &middot; Verified on Clutch",
    "heading": "Real reviews from real engagements. Nothing else.",
    "subheading": "We publish only verified client reviews tied to documented engagements &mdash; currently two, both on Clutch. We do not show an aggregate star rating until we have five or more verified reviews, and we never fabricate testimonials. Independent Certified QuickBooks ProAdvisor firm &mdash; not affiliated with Intuit Inc.",
    "actions": [
      { "label": "Get the free file review", "href": "/quickbooks/file-review/?intent=file-review", "class": "btn--primary" },
      { "label": "Speak to a ProAdvisor", "tel": true, "class": "btn--ghost" }
    ]
  },
  "ctaBand": {
    "eyebrow": "See for yourself",
    "heading": "The best review is your own file, reviewed.",
    "lede": "Start with a free QuickBooks file review by a Certified ProAdvisor &mdash; plain-English findings, optional written fixed-fee scope in three business days. No obligation, no pitch.",
    "actions": [
      { "label": "Get the free file review", "href": "/quickbooks/file-review/?intent=file-review", "class": "btn--primary" },
      { "label": "Book the discovery call", "href": "/contact/?intent=accounting", "class": "btn--ghost" }
    ]
  }
}
---

<section class="section section--compact section--tier-hub" id="reviews-byline">
  <div class="container container--narrow">
    <div class="byline-block">
      <svg class="byline-block__mark" viewBox="0 0 64 64" role="img" aria-label="TechBrot"><rect width="64" height="64" rx="14" fill="#1A1915"></rect><g transform="translate(12.16 12.16) scale(0.62)" fill="#F5F3EC"><path d="M8 10 H38 V54 H26 V22 H8 Z"></path><rect x="42" y="10" width="14" height="12"></rect></g></svg>
      <div>
        <p class="byline-block__name">By the Certified QuickBooks ProAdvisor team</p>
        <p class="byline-block__review">Reviews verified via Clutch &middot; independent firm, not affiliated with Intuit Inc.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="section section--alt" id="reviews-summary">
  <div class="container container--narrow">
    <div class="tldr">
      <p class="tldr__label">The short version</p>
      <h2 class="tldr__heading">Why this page is short &mdash; on purpose.</h2>
      <p class="tldr__body" id="reviews-summary-text">Most accounting and bookkeeping sites lead with review counts and star ratings &mdash; many unverified, self-reported, or fabricated. We don&rsquo;t play that game. TechBrot has <strong>two verified client reviews</strong>, both on <a href="{{ site.clutchProfile }}" rel="noopener" target="_blank">Clutch</a>, each tied to a real, documented engagement. Until we have five or more verified reviews, we publish <strong>no aggregate star rating</strong> &mdash; an honest two beats an inflated fifty. As the verified-review program grows with each completed engagement, real reviews are added here with the same standard.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="section" id="reviews-list">
  <div class="container">
    <header class="section__header">
      <p class="section__eyebrow">Verified reviews</p>
      <h2 class="section__heading">Two real engagements, verified on Clutch.</h2>
      <p class="section__lede">Each review below is published by the client on Clutch and reflects a documented engagement. Follow the link to read it at the source.</p>
    </header>
    <div class="grid-2 stack-8">
      <article class="review-card">
        <blockquote class="review-card__quote">&ldquo;They took something that felt overwhelming to me as a first-year business owner and made it simple.&rdquo;</blockquote>
        <p class="review-card__fact"><strong>The work:</strong> reviewed and corrected QuickBooks records &mdash; reconciling transactions and organizing the chart of accounts.</p>
        <p class="review-card__fact"><strong>The outcome:</strong> books went from disorganized to fully reconciled, delivered on time.</p>
        <div class="review-card__byline">
          <div><span class="review-card__name">Heidi Schubert</span><br><span class="review-card__role">Owner, Beverage Connection &middot; Food &amp; Beverage &middot; Denver, Colorado &middot; via Clutch</span></div>
          <span class="review-card__verified">{% include "icons/check.svg" %}Verified</span>
        </div>
        <a class="review-card__link" href="{{ site.clutchProfile }}" rel="noopener" target="_blank">Read the verified review <span class="lnk-arrow" aria-hidden="true">&rarr;</span></a>
      </article>
      <article class="review-card">
        <blockquote class="review-card__quote">&ldquo;What stood out the most was TechBrot Inc&rsquo;s attention to detail.&rdquo;</blockquote>
        <p class="review-card__fact"><strong>The work:</strong> credit-card reconciliation and financial cleanup &mdash; transaction categorization reviewed and bookkeeping structure improved.</p>
        <p class="review-card__fact"><strong>The outcome:</strong> reporting accuracy and visibility significantly improved.</p>
        <div class="review-card__byline">
          <div><span class="review-card__name">Barbara Best</span><br><span class="review-card__role">CEO, Barbara B. &middot; Business services &middot; California &middot; via Clutch</span></div>
          <span class="review-card__verified">{% include "icons/check.svg" %}Verified</span>
        </div>
        <a class="review-card__link" href="{{ site.clutchProfile }}" rel="noopener" target="_blank">Read the verified review <span class="lnk-arrow" aria-hidden="true">&rarr;</span></a>
      </article>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="section section--alt" id="reviews-standard">
  <div class="container container--narrow">
    <header class="section__header">
      <p class="section__eyebrow">Our review standard</p>
      <h2 class="section__heading">How we handle reviews &mdash; and why.</h2>
    </header>
    <div class="prose">
      <p>A real review program is worth more than a hundred fabricated stars. Every review on this page is published by the client on Clutch, an independent third-party platform, and reflects a documented engagement. We do not write, edit, or incentivize reviews, and we do not display reviews we cannot point you to at the source.</p>
      <p>We withhold an aggregate star rating until at least five verified reviews exist, because a rating built on two data points is not a meaningful average &mdash; showing one would imply more certainty than the evidence supports. When the count reaches five, an honest aggregate will appear here, sourced and dated.</p>
      <p>The verified-review program grows with each completed engagement: clients are invited &mdash; never pressured &mdash; to review the work on Clutch once it&rsquo;s delivered. If you&rsquo;d rather judge the work directly, the most useful next step is a <a href="/quickbooks/file-review/?intent=file-review">free file review</a> &mdash; you see exactly how a Certified ProAdvisor reads your books before any money changes hands.</p>
    </div>
    <p class="meta-reviewed"><span>Published: 2026-06-18</span><span>Updated: 2026-06-18</span><span>Reviewed: 2026-06-18 &middot; Certified QuickBooks ProAdvisor</span></p>
  </div>
</section>
